      "id": "PopularPost41011",
      "post_content": "This guy here is used without any other combos in my Grix' deck; he's basically the main hitter early game, but I've still lost count of how many times this has driven my enemies insane;  \n  \n4th turn: opponent takes 3 and discards a card. ***(^.^)***  \n  \nAlso, the unearth, along with a [Minion Reflector](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Minion Reflector ) makes life in games against hand-reliant decks all the more fun. (for the specter's owner)",
