    {
      "id": "PopularPost90817",
      "post_content": "Goes great in Dredgevine-\n  \nTurn 1. Island, [Hedron Crab](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hedron Crab)   \nTurn 2. [Marsh Flats](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Marsh Flats) into swamp, mill for 6, have hopefully 1 or 2 of unearthers (e.g. this and [Extractor Demon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Extractor Demon)) in graveyard, then play [Renegade Doppelganger](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Renegade Doppelganger).\n  \nTurn 3. Fetch into land, mill for 6 more cards, unearth either this or Extractor Demon, deal either 10 flying damage or 6 flying damage and discard 2, if it connects.",
      "posted_by": "Gomorrah",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost90817\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">Goes great in Dredgevine-\r<br/>Turn 1. Island, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hedron Crab\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hedron Crab\">Hedron Crab</a> <br/>Turn 2. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Marsh Flats\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Marsh Flats\">Marsh Flats</a> into swamp, mill for 6, have hopefully 1 or 2 of unearthers (e.g. this and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Extractor Demon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Extractor Demon\">Extractor Demon</a>) in graveyard, then play <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Renegade Doppelganger\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Renegade Doppelganger\">Renegade Doppelganger</a>.\r<br/>Turn 3. Fetch into land, mill for 6 more cards, unearth either this or Extractor Demon, deal either 10 flying damage or 6 flying damage and discard 2, if it connects.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '90817'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy17647\">Gomorrah</span>\r\n                                (7/25/2010 4:28:34 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rati