    {
      "id": "PopularPost268304",
      "post_content": "It pains me to admit this, but KrosanGardener is right. Megrim does indeed suck. I used it for years. Average amount of damage it got in a game before the opponent cast out their hand was 0-4. One time I lucked out with a [Mind Twist](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Twist) after they played into a huge draw and whacked them for 10 damage, but that was once in years of using it. [Liliana's Caress](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Liliana's Caress) is much improved, but is hurt by sharing casting cost with [Hymn to Tourach](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hymn to Tourach). In short, there was never a time when I was glad to draw this.",
      "posted_by": "blindthrall",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost268304\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">It pains me to admit this, but KrosanGardener is right. Megrim does indeed suck. I used it for years. Average amount of damage it got in a game before the opponent cast out their hand was 0-4. One time I lucked out with a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mind Twist\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Twist\">Mind Twist</a> after they played into a huge draw and whacked them for 10 damage, but that was once in years of using it. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Liliana's Caress\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Liliana's Caress\">Liliana's Caress</a> is much improved, but is hurt by sharing casting cost with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hymn to Tourach\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hymn to Tourach\">Hymn to Tourach</a>. In short, there was never a time when I was glad to draw this.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '268304'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy17415\">blindthrall</span>\r\n                                (9/16/2012 9:25:28 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    R